(1, 'Dr. Rajesh Kumar Jain', 'Principal Director - Surgical Oncology', 'BLK-Max Cancer Center, New Delhi', 'Dr. Rajesh Kumar Jain', 'Dr Rajesh Jain is a distinguished surgical oncologist with over 26 years of experience. He is renowned for his pioneering surgical techniques and unwavering commitment to delivering the highest standard of care.', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">About Dr. Rajesh Kumar Jain</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr Rajesh Jain is a distinguished surgical oncologist with over 26 years of experience. He is renowned for his pioneering surgical techniques and unwavering commitment to delivering the highest standard of care. His expertise spans the treatment of cancers in the head and neck, breast, thoracic, gastrointestinal, gynecological, and urological regions.<br>&nbsp;<br>Dr Jain played an instrumental role in establishing the Departments of Surgical Oncology at both BLK Super Speciality Hospital and Action Cancer Hospital. His contributions included developing standard operating procedures (SOPs), setting up operating theatres, and more.<br>&nbsp;<br>With a strong academic focus, Dr Jain has been actively involved in research projects and the mentorship of junior doctors. Known for his precise surgical skills and compassionate approach, he ensures that patients feel supported at every step of their treatment and recovery journey.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Work Experience</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Presently working as Principal Director - Surgical Oncology at BLK-Max Super Speciality Hospital, New Delhi<br>&nbsp;<br><strong>Previous Experience:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Director &amp; Head - Surgical Oncology, Action Cancer Hospital, New Delhi&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Consultant &amp; Head - Surgical Oncology, BLK Super Speciality Hospital, New Delhi&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Worked in Various Capacities including Consultant - Surgical Oncology, Rajiv Gandhi Cancer Institute, New Delhi&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Registrar - Surgical Oncology, Indraprastha Apollo Hospital, New Delhi</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt 0.5in; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Education &amp; Training</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">MBBS</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">MS (General Surgery)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">DNB (Surgical Oncology)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Membership</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Indian Society of Oncology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Speciality Interest</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Robotic Cancer Surgeries</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Head &amp; Neck Cancer Surgeries</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Breast Cancer Surgeries</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Gynae Cancer Surgeries</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Thoracic and GI Cancer Surgeries</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Uro-Cancer Surgeries</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'docimg.png', 'dr-rajesh-jain'),
(2, 'Dr. Ishan Mohan', 'Director - Head & Neck Oncosurgery', 'BLK-Max Cancer Center, New Delhi', 'Dr. Ishan Mohan', 'Dr Ishan Mohan is a leading Head & Neck Oncosurgeon, dedicated to providing comprehensive and personalized care to patients battling head and neck cancers.', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">About Dr Ishan Mohan</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">With over 23 years of extensive experience, Dr Ishan Mohan is a leading Head &amp; Neck Oncosurgeon, dedicated to providing comprehensive and personalized care to patients battling head and neck cancers. He ensures that every stage of a patient&rsquo;s journey&mdash;from accurate diagnosis to advanced treatment and recovery&mdash;is managed with exceptional skill and unwavering commitment.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Beyond his clinical expertise, Dr Mohan is a prominent figure in medical education. He is an NBE (National Board of Examinations)-certified DrNB (Surgical Oncology) super-speciality teacher and examiner. As one of the first MCh Surgical Oncologists from Tata Memorial Hospital, Mumbai, to begin practicing in North India, he has played a key role in establishing an evidence-based and ethical surgical oncology practice in the region.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Work Experience</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr Ishan Mohan is currently working at Max Healthcare</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Principal Consultant &ndash; Surgical Oncology, Action Cancer Hospital, New Delhi (Sep 2011 &ndash; Jul 2025)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Senior Registrar &ndash; Surgical Oncology, Tata Memorial Hospital, Mumbai and ACTREC (Jul 2008 &ndash; Jul 2011)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Senior Resident &ndash; General Surgery, Maulana Azad Medical College and attached LNJP and GB Pant Hospitals, Delhi (Apr 2005 &ndash; Apr 2008)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Education &amp; Training</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">MCh (Surgical Oncology) &ndash; Tata Memorial Hospital, Mumbai (2011)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">MS (General Surgery) &ndash; Maulana Azad Medical College, Delhi (2005)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">MBBS &ndash; Maulana Azad Medical College, Delhi (2001)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Memberships</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Association of Surgeons of India</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Speciality Interest</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Function Preserving Resections in Head &amp; Neck Cancers</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3D Printed Reconstruction for Head &amp; Neck Cancers</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Transoral Robotic Surgery (TORS)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Robotic Neck Dissection</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Robotic Thyroidectomy</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; fo