(3, 'Dr. Himanshu Gupta', 'Senior Consultant - Plastic & Onco Reconstructive Surgery', 'BLK-Max Cancer Center, New Delhi', 'Dr. Himanshu Gupta', 'Dr Himanshu Gupta is a highly skilled plastic and reconstructive surgeon with advanced expertise in cancer-related reconstruction.', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">About Dr. Himanshu Gupta</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr Himanshu Gupta is a highly skilled plastic and reconstructive surgeon with advanced expertise in cancer-related reconstruction. Driven by a patient-centred approach, Dr. Himanshu integrates innovation, precision, and empathy to deliver personalised treatment and care. His focus areas include breast reconstruction, head and neck restoration, and post-oncologic bone and soft tissue reconstruction.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">In addition to his clinical work, Dr Himanshu actively contributes to surgical education and clinical innovation, with a focus on improving patient outcomes.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Work Experience</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; fon