(6, 'Dr. Shubhi Yadav', 'Senior Consultant - Gynaecological Surgical Oncology', 'BLK-Max Cancer Center, New Delhi', 'Dr. Shubhi Yadav', 'Dr Shubhi Yadav is a dedicated and compassionate gynaecological oncologist with over 14 years of experience in the field.', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">About Dr. Shubhi Yadav</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr Shubhi Yadav is a dedicated and compassionate gynaecological oncologist with over 14 years of experience in the field. She specializes in the accurate diagnosis and personalized management of gynaecologic cancers, offering each patient a tailored treatment plan based on the latest medical advancements and best practices.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">On the academic front, Dr Shubhi Yadav is actively involved in clinical research, contributing to advancements in gynaecologic oncology. She has been an eminent speaker at national and international medical conferences and has authored several articles in reputed journals and medical publications.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Work Experience</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style