e-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Education &amp; Training</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">MBBS</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">DNB (Obstetrics and Gynaecology)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Training (Advanced Laparoscopic Surgery) &ndash; Galaxy Care Hospital, Pune&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Fellowship (Advanced Gynae-Laparoscopy and Gynae-Oncology) &ndash; Galaxy Care Hospital, Pune</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Fellowship (Gynaecologic Oncology) &ndash; Action Cancer Hospital, New Delhi&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Fellowship (Gynaecologic Oncology) &ndash; Universit&auml;tsklinikum Schleswig-Holstein, Kiel, Germany</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Fellowship (Vaginal Hysterectomy) &ndash; Bapat Hospital, Indore</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Fellowship (Operative Hysteroscopy) &ndash; Bapat Hospital, Indore</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Memberships</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-top:0in;list-style-type: disc;list-style-position: outside;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Federation of Obstetric and Gynaecological Societies of India</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Association of Obstetricians and Gynaecologists of Delhi</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Association of Gynaecologic Oncologists of India</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">European Society of Gynaecological Oncology</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">European Network of Young Gynaecologic Oncologists</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">American Society of Clinical Oncology</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">International Society for Fertility